text: Isabel Lucas (born 29 January 1985 in Melbourne) is an Australian actress. She is well known for her role in the soap opera Home and Away, as well as in movies such as Immortals, Transformers: Revenge of the Fallen, Daybreakers, Red Dawn and The Loft. == Other websites == * * Lucas, Isabel on d-nb.info Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Australian movie actors
